{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"402 Payment Required","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Status/402","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>这是一个实验中的功能</strong><br>此功能某些浏览器尚在开发中，请参考<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">浏览器兼容性表格</a>以得到在不同浏览器中适合使用的前缀。由于该功能对应的标准文档可能被重新修订，所以在未来版本的浏览器中该功能的语法和行为可能随之改变。</p></div>\n<p><strong><code>402 Payment Required</code></strong> 是一个被保留使用的非标准客户端错误状态响应码。</p>\n<p>有时，这个状态码表明直到客户端付费之后请求才会被处理。402 状态码被创建最初目的是用于数字现金或微型支付系统，表明客户端请求的内容只有付费之后才能获取。目前还不存在标准的使用约定，不同的实体可以在不同的环境下使用。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"状态","title":"状态","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: plain notranslate\">402 Payment Required\n</pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"响应样例","title":"响应样例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: plain notranslate\">HTTP/1.1 402 Payment Required\nDate: Wed, 21 Oct 2015 07:28:00 GMT\n</pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>规范</th>\n      <th>标题</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc7231#section-6.5.2\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">RFC 7231, section 6.5.2: 402 Payment Required</a></td>\n      <td>HTTP/1.1: Semantics and Content</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"浏览器兼容性","title":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"content":"{{Compat}}"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"相关内容","title":"相关内容","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Authentication\">HTTP authentication</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"状态","id":"状态"},{"text":"响应样例","id":"响应样例"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"相关内容","id":"相关内容"}